# ── Setup checklist ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. Create a project at https://supabase.com
#
# 2. Enable each social provider in:
#    Dashboard → Authentication → Providers
#    All four are FREE to set up:
#
#    - Google:   console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials
#                Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application type).
#                No billing required for OAuth credentials.
#
#    - GitHub:   github.com/settings/developers → OAuth Apps → New OAuth App
#                Completely free. Homepage URL = your GitHub Pages URL.
#
#    - Discord:  discord.com/developers → New Application → OAuth2 tab
#                Completely free.
#
#    - LinkedIn: linkedin.com/developers → Create App → Auth tab
#                Completely free. Requires a LinkedIn Company Page.
#
# 3. Add your GitHub Pages URL to allowed redirect URLs:
#    Dashboard → Authentication → URL Configuration → Redirect URLs
#    e.g. https://your-username.github.io/EbayListingCreator/
#    Also add http://localhost:5173/ for local development.
#
# 4. For Discord & LinkedIn the OAuth callback URL to register in their
#    developer portals is your Supabase URL:
#    https://your-project-id.supabase.co/auth/v1/callback
